Code to monitor network interface status 
It use netlink method.

Complile code : gcc -Wall nw_monitor.c -o nw_monitor

root@ashish:# ./nw_monitor
Started watching:
msg_handler: RTM_NEWLINK
netlink_link_state: Link lo Down
msg_handler: RTM_DELADDR
msg_handler: RTM_NEWLINK
